<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>يَعَاطِ - مثالُ قَطَامِ -: زجرٌ للذئبِ،<span class="c5"> قال:</span><a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>